  "description": "Customize Minecraft's text shadow rendering globally",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/microcontrollers\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"kofi-singular-alt\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/kofi-singular-alt_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://codeberg.org/MicrocontrollersDev/Sciophobia\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"codeberg\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/codeberg_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/sciophobia\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"sinytra connector\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6j289t.svg\">\n</a>\n\n# Sciophobia\n\nCustomize Minecraft's text shadow rendering globally.\n\n## Features\n\n- Hide Text Shadow\n    - Removes text shadow completely. This can help boost performance.\n- Force Text Shadow\n    - Forces shadow on all text globally. Does nothing if Hide Text Shadow is enabled.\n- Alternate Text Shadow\n    - Only translates text shadow down instead of down and to the right.\n- Full Text Shadow\n    - Duplicates the text to simulate the glow outlined text for all text. This will affect performance.",
